<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<module referenceFile="TripleWing Rev A.fzp" moduleId="Adafruit-_0627c4639eef073aa6bcf58e6214b44b_1_0E" fritzingVersion="0.5.2b.02.18.4756">
 <version>4</version>
 <date>2023-06-13</date>
 <author>liz</author>
 <description>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd">
&lt;html>&lt;head>&lt;meta name="qrichtext" content="1" />&lt;style type="text/css">
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style>&lt;/head>&lt;body style=" font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:8.25pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
&lt;p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:13px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#ffffff;">&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; color:#000000; background-color:#ffffff;">This is the&lt;/span>&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; color:#000000;"> &lt;/span>&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; font-weight:496; color:#000000;">FeatherWing Tripler &lt;/span>&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; color:#000000;">- a prototyping add-on and more for all Feather boards. This is similar to our &lt;/span>&lt;a href="https://www.adafruit.com/products/2884">&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; text-decoration: underline; color:#0062c7;">FeatherWing Proto&lt;/span>&lt;/a>&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; color:#000000;"> except there are three! The magic of the Tripler comes when you want to connect your Feather to two other Feather Wings without needing any stacking headers! The Tripler comes with:&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;">&lt;li style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">&lt;span style=" font-size:15px;">1 Tripler Wing PCB&lt;/span>&lt;/li>
&lt;li style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; color:#000000;" style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">&lt;span style=" font-size:15px;">3 sets &lt;/span>&lt;a href="http://www.adafruit.com/products/2886">&lt;span style=" font-size:15px; text-decoration: underline; color:#0062c7;">Feather Female Headers&lt;/span>&lt;/a>&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>
&lt;p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:13px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#ffffff;">&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; color:#000000; background-color:#ffffff;">The Tripler, like the Proto, has three breakouts for each pin on a Feather, as well as a bunch of plain grid proto holes.&lt;/span>&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; color:#000000;"> &lt;/span>&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; font-weight:496; color:#000000;">Also, the three sets of pins are cross connected&lt;/span>&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; color:#000000;"> and for GND and 3.3V, we give you a full strip of connected pads.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:13px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#ffffff;">&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; font-weight:496; color:#000000;">You'll need to solder on the female headers to the PCB, &lt;/span>&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; color:#000000;">the Tripler comes as a mini kit!&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:13px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#ffffff;">&lt;a href="https://www.adafruit.com/feather">&lt;span style=" font-family:'proxima nova','lucida grande','lucida sans unicode','lucida sans','Geneva','Verdana','sans-serif'; font-size:15px; text-decoration: underline; color:#0062c7;">Check out our range of Feather boards here.&lt;/span>&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&lt;/body>&lt;/html></description>
 <title>Adafruit FeatherWing Tripler</title>
